# =========================================================

# NFS Legacy Modpacks - Release 2.0

# .gitignore

#

# Excludes build artifacts, generated files, temporary runtime

# data, installer payloads, and local development files while

# preserving all source code, documentation, templates, and

# repository assets under version control.

