# =========================================================

# Repository notes

# =========================================================

#

# The following directories are intentionally tracked:

#

# releases/**/Gallery/

# screenshots/

#

# These contain release documentation, validation evidence,

# and screenshots used throughout the project.

#

# Generated installers, compressed payloads, temporary runtime

# files, rollback metadata, and local development artifacts are

# intentionally excluded from source control.

#

# Public releases are distributed through:

#

# • GitHub Releases

# • Nexus Mods

#

# Release Engineering:

#

# Version: Release 2.0

# Repository: NFS Legacy Modpacks

